---
title: Crispy Shallot Chorizo Croquettes with Mash, Gravy and Sautéed Green Beans
description: Big texture and bold taste are on the menu tonight! Chorizo and potato patties are breaded with crushed crispy shallot coating, then baked to achieve a cravable crunch. Zucchini, carrots and velvety gravy round out the plate.
